msgctxt "72_Praying Man"
msgid ""
"Please, please, please, make me handsome. Make me handsome. Oh, please..."
msgstr ""
"Ti prego, ti prego, ti prego, rendimi bello. Rendimi bello. Oh, ti prego..."
